dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""I did what?! Can't remember shit,..."
dialogueTree.english: "I did what?! Can't remember shit, I was wasted."

dialogueTree.belarusian: "Што я зрабіў? Нічога не памятаю, я быў збіты".

dialogueTree.english: "Aye', cut that shit out, man."

dialogueTree.english: "Gimme another one!"

dialogueTree.english: "Hey, don't be going soft on me."

dialogueTree.english: "No way I'm going back to Jamrock."

dialogueTree.english: "If it's titties, then Monica's!"

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""The Hardie boys are *unfuckable* n..."

dialogueTree.english: "We could take over the entire city."
dialogueTree.polish: „Moglibyśmy przejąć całe miasto”.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Like a fucking *cobarde*... bitchm..."
dialogueTree.english: "Like a fucking *cobarde*... bitchman-Alain, shit..."

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Survivor guilt my ass, *I* wanted..."
dialogueTree.english: "Survivor guilt my ass, *I* wanted to go that way!"

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""I'm the lucky fuck, who didn't tak..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'm the lucky fuck, who didn't take a scratch." (Sighs.)
dialogueTree.polish: „Jestem fartowny skurwiel, którego nawet nie tknęli” – mówi, wzdychając.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я шчаслівы сволач, якога нават не кранулі" – кажа ён, уздыхаючы.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Shanky's gonna get a lesson in Boo..."
dialogueTree.english: "Shanky's gonna get a lesson in Boogie Street justice."

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Gonna hunt that rat-faced fuck dow..."
dialogueTree.english: "Gonna hunt that rat-faced fuck down."
dialogueTree.polish: „Muszę dorwać tego skurwiałego szczura”.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""For Titus... for Glenny... for......"
dialogueTree.english: "For Titus... for Glenny... for... for Titus!!!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Za Titusa... za Glenny'ego... Za... za Titusa!!!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "За Тытуса... за Глені... За... за Тытуса!!!"

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""When it's done I'll just blow my b..."
dialogueTree.english: "When it's done I'll just blow my brains out... Fuck everything."
dialogueTree.polish: „Jak to się skończy, to se po prostu odstrzelę łeb... Jebać to wszystko”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Як гэта скончыцца, дык проста адстрэлю сабе галаву... Усім начхаць на гэта".

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Boogie street justice. Gonna make..."
dialogueTree.english: "Boogie street justice. Gonna make you proud, T."
dialogueTree.polish: „Sprawiedliwość rodem z Boogie Street. Będziesz ze mnie dumny, T”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Справядлівасць родам з Бугі Стрыт. Ты будзеш ганарыцца мною, Т".
